"{\"uid\": \"www.accountingtoday.com.-news-tax-practice-what-brexit-is-likely-to-mean-for-taxes-trade-and-more-78516-1-html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"IMGCAP(1)]Regardless of whether you were surprised, overjoyed, dismayed or showed any other emotion (perhaps anger as you saw world markets tank), Brexit is here.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brexit\", \"score\": 0.9754341357548612, \"rank\": 0.02509710081714367, \"text\": \"Brexit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brexit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brexit\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, we are talking about the British exit from the European Union.\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not sure why the media coined the term \\\"Brexit,\\\" when it's not only Britain (England and Wales) that voted, but the United Kingdom, which includes Great Britain, Scotland and Northern Ireland, with the latter two not referring to themselves as \\\"British.\\\"\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But we digress.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the UK did not buy into the monetary union and continued to use the Pound Sterling as its currency, it played an active and necessary role in the EU.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the June 23rd vote to exit the EU, there seem to be more questions than answers.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But first, some facts:  Per the BBC, England voted strongly for Brexit by a 53.4 percent to 46.6 percent margin.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wales had a similar outcome, 52.5 percent to 47.5 percent.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Scotland and Northern Ireland both voted to stay, with Scottish supporters garnering 62 percent and Northern Ireland supporters reaching 55.8 percent.\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What Scotland and Northern Ireland have in mind is unclear.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If they prefer to remain part of the EU, as some suggest, will they also want to remain a part of the UK?\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or will Scotland and Northern Ireland continue to push for autonomy?\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The UK has two years to negotiate its withdrawal.\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While a lot can happen in that timeframe, let us assume the UK truly exits.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What's next?\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What's the Future of the UK?\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Suppose Scotland and Northern Ireland secede from the UK.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As far as the tax world, they currently operate under the UK system.\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Note the tax treaty that people often refer to as the \\\"UK-US tax treaty\\\" is called Convention between the Government of the United States of America and the Government of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital Gains.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1974, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, the treaty is with all of the UK: Great Britain (England, Scotland, Wales) and Northern Ireland.\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If Scotland and Northern Ireland leave the UK, presumably the treaty would not apply to their residents.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, they would have to negotiate their own tax treaties.\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(When Hong Kong became part of China, it did not become part of the China-US tax treaty.)\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In another example though, the treaties with the USSR and Czechoslovakia were extended for a period of time to the states included in each prior to their break-ups into separate sovereign states.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[IMGCAP(2)]If you are a US company with a parent, subsidiary or affiliate in Scotland or Northern Ireland, it may be wise to examine your structure and costs in any potential reorganization.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One must bear in mind that the \\\"clock does not begin to tick\\\" until the UK invokes Article 50 of the EU treaty, giving official notice of its exit.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once invoked, it will take at least two years to fully complete the exit.\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Depending on the impact and cost, we envision that companies may choose to relocate to ensure treaty benefits.\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How Will Customs Duties Change?\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once the UK exits, the EU customs duties rules will no longer apply.\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, absent trade agreements between the UK and the EU or its members, there are likely to be duties charged on UK-EU trade.\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The UK may also enter agreements with other countries and/or trade blocs.\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In theory, UK-EU negotiations would lead to small, if any, duties, but the administrative headaches could be substantial.\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Furthermore, any trade agreements between the EU and other non-EU countries may be affected and/or subject to renegotiation.\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3601, \"entities\": []}]}"